author: trawick
msg: Clean up compile warnings, mostly by including apr_strings.h.

author: trawick
msg: Fix problems with APR sockaddr handling on Win32.  It didn't always
return the right information on the local socket address.  This
change uses the Unix logic for delaying/avoiding getsockname() to
ensure that it is done when needed.

author: trawick
msg: ap_recv() on Win32: Set bytes-read to 0 on error.
